Package com.betleopard

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Builder<T>  
    DomainFactory<T>
    High-level interface to describe the domain object factories - allows pluggable implementations (including Hazelcast, simple Java 8, Spark)
    JSONSerializable
    High-level interface to indicate that a domain type is serializable to JSON using Jackson.
    LongIndexed
    A simple interface for domain objects, which are expected to be indexed by a long value that represents the ID of the object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomLegSerializer
    Serializer class for bet legs.
    Utils
    Holder for associated helper methods
    Utils.RaceCostComparator
    Helper class, needed because the comparator needs to be serializable, and yet needs to be stateless and not a lambda
    Utils.Reaper
    A helper class that can be used to recursively delete and clean up the temp dir
